(87, '95f33bba-f682-4f98-8b4f-f4c659ec7d8d', 2, 'Update', 'App\\Product', 36, 'App\\Product', 36, 'App\\Product', 36, '', 'finished', '', '2022-03-31 09:31:57', '2022-03-31 09:31:57', '{\"benefits\":\"The nature-identical Evicide\\u00ae rose is a fragrance component and antimicrobial. The delicate floral scent of rose can mask undesired odors in the formulation without using fragrance. On top it has a distinct antimicrobial effect against yeast and mold and can especially help to protect products when fungi are difficult to control.\",\"applications\":\"Evicide\\u00ae rose is perfect for modern and mild skin care formulations, also fragrance free ones. It is especially powerful against fungi in all emulsion types and works already at 0.3% to improve the performance of any preservative system. \",\"usage_level\":\"0.1 - 0.5%\",\"is_natural\":0,\"cosmos_compliant\":0,\"seo\":null}', '{\"benefits\":\"The nature-identical Evicide\\u00ae rose is a fragrance component and antimicrobial. The delicate floral scent of rose can mask undesired odors in the formulation without using fragrance. On top it has a distinct antimicrobial effect against yeast and mold and can especially help to protect products when fungi are difficult to control. At higher dosage, e.g. 1% it can fully protect personal care products agains microbial spoilage.\",\"applications\":\"Evicide\\u00ae rose is perfect for modern and mild skin care formulations, also fragrance free ones. It is especially powerful against fungi in all emulsion types and works already at low dosage to improve the performance of any preservative system.\",\"usage_level\":\"0.1 - 1.0%\",\"is_natural\":false,\"cosmos_compliant\":false,\"seo\":\"{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Evicide\\\\u00ae rose - nature identical multifunctional ingredient for cosmetics\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Evicide\\\\u00ae rose (INCI Phenethylalcohol) has many interesting functions in personal care products. As a part of the natural scent of roses Phenethylalcohol imparts a delicate fragrance to finished products as well as a strong antimicrobial effect. In many products this makes the use of preservatives obsolete.\\\"}\"}'),
